{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c60461b6c5","title":"对《核子劫后生机未灭》一文的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"34b2df0946","index":0,"year":1964,"month":12,"day":25,"articleId":"c60461b6c5"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji47","name":"毛泽东全集第47卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/47-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji47":{"comments":[{"id":"d14b7cdac1","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"c60461b6c5","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东对中共中央军委秘书长、中国人民解放军总参谋长、国务院副总理罗瑞卿1964年12月24日星送信的批语。"},{"id":"d61f16f522","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"c60461b6c5","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指罗瑞卿呈送的香港《新闻天地》刊载的一篇题为《核子动后生机未灭》的署名通讯。通讯说：就科学家理论上而言，核子爆炸后的地区，因大量辐射尘的浸染，将寸草不生，动物灭绝。最近美国科学家一行，回到六年来被封锁的西太平洋比基尼岛和恩利威吐克环“核子靴场”时，却见杂花生树、好鸟飞鸣、鼠跳鱼跃、海藻漂浮，而莫不惊叹大自然在动后复苏的伟大活力了。才知道所谓“核子爆炸后放射性永久存在，将使一切动植物的生机绝灭”的说法，未免过甚其辞。"},{"id":"22760b48ba","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"c60461b6c5","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"罗瑞卿1964年12月27日致信中共中央书记处书记、中共北京市委书记、北京市市长彭真：主席口头指示，此件可作为参考资料发给中央工作会议同志和人大代表。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c56da2ffd5","type":"title","text":"对《核子动后生机未灭》一文的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"c60461b6c5"},{"id":"d14b7cdac1","type":"paragraph","text":"已阅。退罗瑞卿同志","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"c60461b6c5"},{"id":"d61f16f522","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"c60461b6c5"},{"id":"22760b48ba","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月二十五日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"c60461b6c5"}],"page":{"id":"c313973e76","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"c60461b6c5","start":343,"end":343}}}},"__N_SSG":true}